name: AwesomeOldQosmeticsModelInstaller
description:
Allows you to install .qsaber, .qwall and .qbloq files using ModsBeforeFriday and other modding tools

NOTE: These formats are outdated. Instead you should use .whacker, .cyoob and .box files if possible instead.
author: jxnxsdev
description_zh:
能让你在ModsBeforeFriday或其它模组工具上安装.qsaber, .qwall以及.qbloq格式的文件。

注意：这些格式已经过时了。你应该尽量用.whacker, .cyoob和.box文件。
